frames.input.event

Class MotionEvent6

  • java.lang.Object
    • frames.input.Event
      • frames.input.event.MotionEvent
        • frames.input.event.MotionEvent6

  • public class MotionEvent6
extends MotionEvent
    A MotionEvent with six degrees-of-freedom ( x(), y(), z() , rx(), ry() and rz()).
